template.value: User Access Review Admin App

This application was built to help setup a new review cycle for SOX User Access Review (UAR). In this application you can
1. Add employees and who is going to review their access reviews
2. Manage the system roles that will be generated as part of the quarterly audit
3. Create new review cycles. The creation process will do two things, insert a cycle into the database and also create a record for each role and employee combination.

*For example if you have two roles and three employees, it will create 6 records where each employee has two roles to be removed*
Are you sure you want to revoke all {{table1.selectedRow.data.length}} selected user role combinations? The reasons below along with a revokation request, will be applied to all selected roles.

template.label: Why was this access appropriate to begin with:
_captionByIndex: The job/role this person had required this access, but their job and or responsibilities changed
This was an error in the first place.

template.label: Why are you removing/changing access now:
_captionByIndex: The person has transitioned to a different role recently
The functionality provided by this role is no longer needed / legacy permissions
This individual has left the company

template.query: SELECT * FROM system_roles ORDER BY name;
SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY name;
SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY name;

INSERT INTO ACCESS_REVIEWS (
  STATUS,
  EMPLOYEE_EMAIL,
  REVIEW_CYCLE_ID,
  SYSTEMROLE_ID, 
  INITIALDECISIONREASON,
  UPDATED_AT,
  "ACTION",
  REASON
)
  SELECT
    'Action Required',
    employees.email,
    review_cycles.id,
    system_roles.id,
    access_reviews.INITIALDECISIONREASON,
    {{ moment().toISOString() }},
    access_reviews.action,
    ''
  FROM review_cycles
  CROSS JOIN employees
  CROSS JOIN system_roles
  LEFT JOIN access_reviews ON 
    access_reviews.employee_email = employees.email 
    AND access_reviews.systemrole_id = system_roles.id
    AND access_reviews.review_cycle_id = review_cycles.id
  WHERE review_cycles.id = {{ getLastReviewCycleInserted.data.ID[0] }}

options.title: Create Access Reviews
options.description: Created a new access review for each role and each employee

template.query: SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY name;
SELECT * FROM system_roles ORDER BY name;
SELECT id from review_cycles ORDER BY id desc LIMIT 1;
